<template>
  <NavBar/>
  <router-view/>
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'
import NavBar from "./NavBar.vue"
export default {
  components: {
    NavBar
  },
  created() {
    this.$http = axios.create({
      baseURL: 'https://badsite.com',
      headers: {
        Authorization: `Bearer ${this.$store.getters.StateToken}`
      }
    })
  }
}
</script>

<style>

  text-align: center;
  color: #2c3e50;
}

nav {
  padding: 30px;
}

nav a {
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #2c3e50;
}

nav a.router-link-exact-active {
  color: #42b983;
}
</style>
